        <span content="2008-02-18" class="main-meta">2008-02-18 06:02:11</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://movie.douban.com/review/1306705/">几个好细节（剧透慎入）</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1306705_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1306705">
